---
layout: invasion
title: Invasion Events
javascripts: [ http://cdn.lanyrd.net/badges/person-v1.min.js ]
---
%p We've found <strong>#{site.sessions.length}</strong> upcoming sessions about Arquillian (courtesy <a href="http://lanyrd.com">lanyrd.com</a>). If you know of an upcoming session taking place that's not shown here, please add it to lanyrd.com to help promote it.
#sessions
- for session in site.sessions
  .session
    %h2
      %a{:href=>session.detail_url}= session.title
    %p.meta
      #{session.start_datetime.strftime('%b %d, %Y - %I:%M%p')} to #{session.end_datetime.strftime('%I:%M%p')} #{session.timezone}
      at
      %a{:href=>session.event_url}= session.event
      in #{session.event_location}
    = session.description
    - if !session.speaker_names.empty?
      %p.speakers <strong>Speakers:</strong> #{session.speaker_names.join(', ')}
- speakers = { 'aslakknutsen' => { :name => 'Aslak', :gravatar=>'3f27861ec08730fd02c91fe4129d2668' }, 'mojavelinux' => { :name=>'Dan', :gravatar=>'dcccd96c499963133f7f95e7ffa20c4e' }, 'alrubinger' => { :name => 'Andrew', :gravatar=>'4369758fcee235bebd875f0de34aa42e' } }
%h2 Arquillian Roadies
%p Below are a list of upcoming speaking events for the members of the Arquillian team.
- speakers.each do |username, person|
  %h3
    %img{:src=>"http://gravatar.com/avatar/#{person[:gravatar]}?s=48", :alt=>person[:name], :style=>'vertical-align: middle; border: 3px double #ccc;'}
    = person[:name]
  .lanyrd-target-splat
    %a.lanyrd-splat.lanyrd-template-detailed{ :href=>"http://lanyrd.com/profile/#{username}/", :rel=>'me' } See all of #{person[:name]}'s upcoming appearances &raquo;
